== Bio

I am a MASc student specializing in machine learning and GAI-driven wireless communication. I received my B.Sc. in Computer Science and Statistics from York University, where I pursue my master degree under the supervision of [https://sites.google.com/view/ngwn-research-lab/home Prof. Hina Tabassum] and [https://www.eecs.yorku.ca/~pingw/ Prof. Ping Wang].

Currently, my work explores resource-aware communication strategies, quantum-enhanced user association, and hybrid large language model (LLM)-assisted decision-making for joint driving and communication optimization.

